proof:
Proof using.
    unfold iord. iord_dom_unfolder; ins; cintuition.
    rewrite restr_relE; iorder.
    destruct a; rewrite no_sb_to_init, no_fi_to_init; try discriminate.
    specialize CONS with (G := G) (sc := actid ⋃ (sc_dom (wf_sbE WF) (wf_sfE WF))).
    intros [a [a_sb a_rf a_fw a_ar a_iprog]].
    simpl. apply CONS; simpl.
    eapply iord_simpl_irreflexive; eauto.
    revert COMP WFSC CONS. apply complete_set_inv, irreflexive_to_complete; auto; iorder.
    intros. rewrite iord_alt. iorder. apply irreflexive_restr; simpl.
    apply iord_simpl_irreflexive; auto.
Qed.
